{"tid":1474283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（818後續）全球連線手牽手人鏈","createTime":"2019-08-15T06:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T02:32:03.000Z","uid":154277,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4becc85c4b0127816ea340d29247cc1edb2ff390","tid":1474283,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"機場之後，我地終於獲得全球正視<br />\n我地而家最需要嘅係：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港受害者形象-&gt;國際持續注視-&gt;向中國施壓</span><br />\n下一步除咗818百萬大遊行，我覺得李怡之前提過的手牽手人鏈係可以考慮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢種和平大愛畫面震撼的示威，外國媒體最愛</span><br />\n如果做到全球連線，例如台灣、全球港人一齊圍，圍地標／中國大使館／聯合國總部呢啲，noise一定好大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38c63549eedbf156f4babef321d6623fe897b37","tid":1474283,"uid":8948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"當外國做緊立法工作<br />\n我地要做好形象工程<br />\n一齊唱us國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />表示支持民主同自由"},{"pid":"2d724815949d4c4ea6ad1b3ef78c9e8efb76e2e6","tid":1474283,"uid":283738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9391178cd73ce703558313ee69381a39704c440","tid":1474283,"uid":307212,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4becc85c4b0127816ea340d29247cc1edb2ff390","tid":1474283,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"機場之後，我地終於獲得全球正視<br />\n我地而家最需要嘅係：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港受害者形象-&gt;國際持續注視-&gt;向中國施壓</span><br />\n下一步除咗818百萬大遊行，我覺得李怡之前提過的手牽手人鏈係可以考慮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢種和平大愛畫面震撼的示威，外國媒體最愛</span><br />\n如果做到全球連線，例如台灣、全球港人一齊圍，圍地標／中國大使館／聯合國總部呢啲，noise一定好大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"同意可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---轉載自Facebook Strange Joanne---<br />\n<br />\n【打游擊、遊行、靜坐以外，仲有其他抗爭手法？】<br />\n<br />\n即係話冇諗到邊條計最好嘅時候，<br />\n咩都要試下！遊行試過，佔領試過，游擊又打緊。<br />\n<br />\n勇敢嘅前線手足好攰了，<br />\n200萬裡面和平嘅市民，你哋做緊乜呀？<br />\n坐係屋企話大家方向唔啱嘅同時，<br />\n係咪可以試吓用另一種抗爭手法呢？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人聽過「自由人鏈」又稱「波羅的海之路」(The Baltic Way or The Chain of Freedom)？<br />\n<br />\n其實係發生於1989年8月23日的一次和平示威，同香港情況一樣，這一示威是為了希望世界能夠關心三國共同的歷史遭遇，佢哋嘅目的自己可以睇wikipeadia。<br />\n<br />\n具體做法：：200多萬民眾為擺脫蘇聯的專制統治走上街頭，手拉手、唱著歌組成了一條穿越波羅的海三國的600多公里長的人鏈。<br />\n<br />\n好處：和平 / 冇咁阻街/ 有影響力/ 畫面靚/ 接觸面廣/ 參與度高<br />\n<br />\n社會運動家藉此宣揚：<br />\n蘇聯佔領三國是不合法的，<br />\n三國獨立並非政治議題，而是道德議題。<br />\n<br />\n同而家香港情況都類似，<br />\n警察濫權已經上升到道德層面，<br />\n所以繼續擴大和平聲音可以做到「靚畫面」，<br />\n藉此宣揚5大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n東歐國家、蘇聯國內和臺灣都相繼舉行過類似示威，如2004年約有200萬臺灣民眾參與的228百萬人手牽手護台灣。<br />\n<br />\n有冇用？唔知。<br />\n老套嗰句，坐喺度，冇用就梗嘅！<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會愛沙尼亞議員克蘭(Tunne Kelam)說：<br />\n「對我來說，最開始的起點就是為自己的尊嚴、人的氣節而戰。當時還只是嘗試，我們都不知道之後會發生什麼，這是個冒險。當然了，假如不敢冒險，就什麼也做不到。」"},{"pid":"ca56d22cc0cfd2dc5efa9393b0b331ccf7d17966","tid":1474283,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到有人睇<br />\n10"},{"pid":"a4102fae59128eb76e93311d55d76b7ef0d9ee14","tid":1474283,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"9<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37508a48a82414771675046a2bbcf1d36781eee3","tid":1474283,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:32:42.000Z","msg":"8<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e7463d2e332f23e0a39f532be9131b4c3b5346","tid":1474283,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:32:49.000Z","msg":"Do you hear the people sing?"},{"pid":"54f5a543c959b107bd6aaf846fec80851591f406","tid":1474283,"uid":14370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2547734ba31094d51032f2a9d35d7021d8b86486","tid":1474283,"uid":7438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"可以一試"},{"pid":"9ee9fcb4d7fcf720e0ebe6c55673db8bcfc694ab","tid":1474283,"uid":98141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:36:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b60cc2592c297dfa1c738e252c6458f7436ad231","tid":1474283,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:37:58.000Z","msg":"7<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510c97a412c7f7670ddc7a0ee9ce02310d0d7c3d","tid":1474283,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"6<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210534255f3ae46b10eee3bb6454ea850a432201","tid":1474283,"uid":296855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">try</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">try</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" c